                                "byte_start": 81858,
                                "byte_stop": 133580,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in No. 91-871, Bath Iron Works Corporation versus the Director of the Office of Workers\u0027 Compensation Programs will be announced by Justice Stevens."
                            }
